he chest at a petrol station on Wednesday night and the assailants drove off in his vehicle.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While waiting to be served by the petrol attendant, he was confronted by two armed males,\\\" police spokesperson Lieutenant Colonel Mavela Masondo told reporters on Thursday, adding no arrests had yet been made.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Centre-back Fleurs played every minute for South Africa at the Tokyo Summer Olympics in 2021, and that same year was called up to the senior team for World Cup qualifiers against Ethiopia, though he did not make it off the bench and was uncapped.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.960627746898372, \"rank\": 0.040985908797406115, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9020145652258763, \"rank\": 0.10845122977848425, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We woke up to the heartbreaking and devastating news of the passing of this young life.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is such a huge loss for his family, friends, his teammates and football in general.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all grieving this young man's passing,\\\" South African Football Association president Danny Jordaan said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1